description:
Our budding director Kaden has found himself a fellow Texan in Jakub, a compact fellow who stands 5'6' and weighs in at 150 lbs. (I'll save you the google searching if you don't know -- it's taking a 4x4 truck out and driving through sloppy mud. So basically -- Jakub likes it dirty. Yeah, I know, he didn't say that -- but just work with me here!)

After we get the introductions out of the way, Kaden lets Jakub go to work. He quickly loses his clothes and find out he's got quite a bit of ink covering up his mostly smooth body. And, a nice looking dick, too! I have to say, this is one of those videos where watching the model in action is better than the photos. Jakub comes alive in a moving image and it's sexy to see him gyrate and work himself over for Kaden and the camera.
title: Jakub
